articles.description: Kenneth Ogbe scored 22 points with four 3-pointers, Brandon Randolph added 17 points, and Utah Valley snapped New Mexico State's 11-game win streak with an 86-79 victory on Thursday night.
articles.headline: Utah Valley beats New Mexico State 86-79

articles.description: Anthony Duruji scored 21 points and swatted 3 shots and Daquan Bracey added 11 points as Louisiana Tech pulled away to beat UAB 73-60 on Thursday night.
articles.headline: Duruji and Bracey help Bulldogs escape Blazers

articles.description: Jonathan Stark played all 40 minutes and scored 32 points with five assists and four rebounds to propel Murray State past Jacksonville State 68-60 on Thursday night for its eighth straight victory.
articles.headline: Murray State tops Jacksonville State for eighth straight win

articles.description: Darral Willis Jr. and Shaquille Morris lead the Shockers to a huge 93-86 victory against Temple.
articles.headline: Willis sinks 24 points in Shockers' victory

images.caption: Darral Willis Jr. and Shaquille Morris lead the Shockers to a huge 93-86 victory against Temple.
images.name: Willis sinks 24 points in Shockers' victory

articles.description: Michael Ertel and Sam McDaniel combined for 39 points as Louisiana-Monroe rolled over UT Arlington 84-71 to get its third straight Sun Belt Conference victory on Thursday night.
articles.headline: UL Monroe rolls over UT Arlington 84-71

articles.description: Cincinnati, Purdue and Ohio State each entered the night a projected top-four seed. But each team lost a stumper, and now they're unsure.
articles.headline: Sunday's seed announcement was fun, but Thursday was real
